re\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n        <div id=\"main\"><!-- START / MAIN BLOCK -->\n        \t<div id=\"header_menu\">\n    <div id=\"header_c\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/company/\">会社概要</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/soshikizu/\">組織図</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\t\t\t\n\t\t\t            <div class=\"page_title\">\n            \t<img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/themes/folkart-pc/images/title_shop2.gif\" width=\"103\" height=\"20\" alt=\"店舗情報\" class=\"left\" />\n                <p class=\"right\"><a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/\">ホーム</a>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/shop_info\">店舗情報</a>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<span>びいどろ 太宰府店</span></p>\n            \t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"post\"><!-- START / POST BLOCK -->\n                <div class=\"post_main\"><!-- START / SINGLEPOST(POST-LEFT) BLOCK -->\n                    <h1>びいどろ 太宰府店</h1>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"slide_image\">\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/4c3100fec16980423a19eab42e6e1953.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/f16e516520daa408bf5ac413eaa817e8.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/44d22270a295e9a7e4844fa4d32ca644.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/530028816c10d7a16373b5dcc6a090cc.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/663d6c020546064e385f48a05e75b71e.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/e0775e55b9452b731ebaa564d4103aed.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/12779df06c76b27a644f81b5839b2663.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2eabd59e6e1e0a77326bfeab681a54a6.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/70f3e5adb9090336f1d339d25028732b.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n <li><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/b558f0f67d9d622843b48a965bb4ffb7.jpg\" width=\"799\" height=\"600\" /></li>\n</ul>\n                    <div class=\"clear\" style=\"height:20px;\"></div>\n                    \n                    <p>太宰府天満宮の参道沿いにあるびいどろ太宰府店は、<br />\nミニガラスをはじめ根付、お守り、グラスなど<br />\n太宰府限定商品を豊富に取り揃えております。<br />\n干支物・ひな祭り・端午の節句など、季節のガラス工芸品はリピーター様も多いです◎<br />\nぜひ非日常なキラキラ空間をお楽しみください！</p>\n                </div><!-- END / SINGLEPOST(POST-LEFT) BLOCK -->\n                        \n                <div class=\"post_side\"><!-- START / POSTSIDE(POST-RIGHT) BLOCK -->\n                    <div class=\"new_arrival_title\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/biidorodazaifu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/themes/folkart-pc/images/shop_Instagram.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"136\" height=\"30\" /></a>\n                    </div>\n                        <span class=\"basic_info\">\n                            <p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/biidorodazaifu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">びいどろ 太宰府店<img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/themes/folkart-pc/images/external_link.png\" alt=\"インスタグラム\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" style=\"padding-left:5px;\" /></a></p>\n                        </span>\n\n                    <div class=\"new_arrival_title\">\n                        <img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/themes/folkart-pc/images/title_shopinfo.gif\" alt=\"基本情報\" width=\"76\" height=\"14\" />\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"basic_info\">\n                        <h6>【住所】</h6>\n                        <p>〒818-0117<br />\n福岡県太宰府市宰府2-7-17</p>\n                        <h6>【電話】</h6>\n                        <p>092-922-3611</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>【営業時間】</h6>\n                        <p>平日　　10：00～17：30<br />\n土日祝　10：00～18：00</p>\n                        <h6>【定休日】</h6>\n                        <p>年中無休</p>\n                        <p><strong>【周辺地図】</strong>（<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=びいどろ 太宰府店\" target=\"\">拡大</a>）</p>\n                    </span>\n                  <iframe width=\"230\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=びいどろ 太宰府店&amp;output=embed&iwloc=\"></iframe>\n                </div><!-- END / POSTSIDE(POST-RIGHT) BLOCK -->\n                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n            </div><!-- END / POST BLOCK -->\n            \n            <div class=\"relatedpost_box\"><!-- START / RELATEDTHUMBS BLOCK -->\n                <div class=\"title_related\"><img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/wp-content/themes/folkart-pc/images/title_related.gif\" width=\"96\" height=\"16\" alt=\"関連する記事\" /></div>\n                   \n                    <div class='yarpp-related'>\n\n\t    <a href=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/news/20120915180405_4526.html\" class=\"news_thumb\">\n        <div class=\"news_thumb_inner\">\n            <p class=\"thum_date\">2012/09/15&nbsp;18:04</p>\n            <div class=\"news_thumb_img\">\n            \t<img src=\"https://www.folkart.co.jp/system/phpThumb/phpThumb.php?src=/system/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/d0890a3f3e8d0687942abbafc800c3c42-240x180.jpg&amp;w=210&amp;h=140&amp;zc=1&amp;q=75\" />            </div>\n            <d